**The Atlas**, published by GenAI.Works on LinkedIn, is the largest AI newsletter on the platform with 3,151,421 subscribers as of April 2026. Among the email newsletters in this guide, **TLDR AI** leads with over 1.25M subscribers delivered daily.

Are there good free AI newsletters?

