For most professionals, 3–5 newsletters is optimal. We recommend one community/LinkedIn newsletter (The Atlas), one daily digest (TLDR AI for engineers or The Neuron for multi-industry teams), and one role-specific newsletter from the comparison table above. Adding more beyond five typically leads to inbox fatigue without additional insight.

